---
// Legacy unprefixed URL — content lives in
// src/content/pages/modules/distributions/{en,ko}.mdx, served at
// /en/modules/distributions/ and /ko/modules/distributions/. We keep this
// file as a redirect stub (rather than 404) for any external bookmark
// or internal link that points at the unprefixed URL. Astro emits static
// redirect HTML with meta refresh + canonical + robots:noindex.
return Astro.redirect("/en/modules/distributions/", 301);
